WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.838
"Osetih pogreb u svom mozgu

00:00:07.838 --> 00:00:10.240
i ožalošćene kako dolaze i odlaze,

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:12.900
koračaju, koračaju, dok ne osetih

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:15.836
da razum puca.

00:00:15.836 --> 00:00:17.605
A kada su svi seli,

00:00:17.605 --> 00:00:19.603
poče služba, kao bubanj,

00:00:19.603 --> 00:00:22.315
koji bije, bije

00:00:22.315 --> 00:00:25.831
dok mi um ne utrnu.

00:00:25.831 --> 00:00:27.707
I tada čuh kako podižu kovčeg

00:00:27.707 --> 00:00:29.994
i škripe po mojoj duši

00:00:29.994 --> 00:00:33.053
istim onim olovnim čizmama iznova,